abstract = {In summer, fans and air conditioners are essential cooling equipment for people. Air conditioners are better at cooling than fans and can quickly lower indoor temperatures. But air conditioning also has the disadvantages of higher price, large volume and inconvenient to carry, while the fan is a low-cost, convenient to carry cooling equipment. However, traditional fans not only have few functions, but also need to be manually controlled and adjusted, resulting in low intelligence. Therefore, in view of the disadvantages of traditional fans, such as manually switching machine, adjusting wind speed and single function, this paper introduces an intelligent temperature controlled human body induction fan. The induction fan uses temperature sensor DS18B20 to detect the temperature change, selects the audion as the driving part, and then controls by STC89C52 MCU. External buttons are set to set the upper and lower limits of temperature, and the pyroelectric sensor is used to realize the human body induction function. Display detection temperature and tap on LCD1602 LCD screen. The fan detects the presence of the human body according to the sensor and determines whether to turn on or off intelligently. If the detected temperature reaches the set value, the induction fan will automatically switch the corresponding gear to change the wind speed.Finally, the feasibility and practicability of the design are verified by the test. Compared with traditional fans, this design saves time and energy, and is more convenient to use in daily life.},
